messages.message: If table extraction is selected, shouldn't it always show as a table vs. in markdown? cc: @Kaustubh (KD) @lydia
They should show up as Markdown, I know this happens occasionally but curious why cc: @danny.lan in case you have insight here

with table extraction it should show up as a table but it looks like there is an extra vertical bar character which is preventing the output from being rendered as a table.

re @Vishnu regarding the table output format, do you know why there might be a discrepancy?
